───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Modifications to libopus in this distribution
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The libopus sources have been vendored as-is from the v1.5.2 release, with
the following exceptions to reduce repository size (these directories are
not required at runtime):

  - dnn/torch/         (PyTorch training scripts for DNN models)
  - dnn/training_tf2/  (TensorFlow training scripts for DNN models)
  - doc/               (HTML documentation, regenerable from source)
  - tests/             (libopus internal test suite)
  - training/          (Auxiliary training scripts)

The runtime C and header files (celt/, silk/, src/, include/, dnn/ runtime,
cmake/, m4/, meson/, scripts/) are preserved unmodified.

No modifications to the libopus source code itself have been made. All
optimizations and SIMD code paths are configured at build time via Zig.

